+### Minimal Configuration with Coturn {#module-services-netbird-server-quickstart-coturn}
+
+This is the traditional setup using Coturn as the TURN server:
 
 ```nix
 {
@@ -19,7 +21,6 @@ There are quite a few settings that need to be passed to Netbird for it to funct
 
     coturn = {
       enable = true;
-
       passwordFile = "/path/to/a/secret/password";
     };
 
@@ -42,3 +43,172 @@ There are quite a few settings that need to be passed to Netbird for it to funct
